oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Ruth Robb Finney
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Portrait of Ruth Robb Finney in light colored gown.
Ruth Robb Finney (1881-?) was the daughter of George P. Finney & Eliza H. Robb, of 205 Woodland St. in East Nashville. She married Rev. William Burnside Campbell (1886-?) in Nashville on 10/6/1909.
